race.comment: ALL ADORE (12) improving filly from the Nick Olive yard who jumps a few grades today from the sticky draw. Returned excellent figures when she gave them a galloping lesson over 1000m at Sapphire Coast as fav in slick time. Gets in light with the claim and can measure up if she gets across early. LADY OLENNA (10) underrated mare fourth-up for this after catching the eye in this class at all three runs. Will appreciate the good tempo with Nock's claim. Leading each way player. MOVE SHE CAN (11) has returned a much stronger mare and starting to build a tidy winning CV. Stalked the speed when saluting as fav over 1150m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Has further upside to come and gets map favours. MISS REBEL (3) good second-up performer back in top shape after shouldering the 60kg when second over 1150m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Sure to be thereabouts. LYRICAL BEAUTY (17) can measure up to these with the big weight drop. Each way.
